The first and only full-body fractional technology for subdermal adipose remodeling (SARDS). Despite being applied externally, it offers the deepest fractional technology, allowing a physician or aesthetic provider to target deep layers of a patientтАЩs skin and remodel collagen.

KEY BENEFITS:
Deep and safe fractional treatment penetrating 4000 microns with an additional thermal profile of 1000+ microns.

can be extended to the entire body.

BENEFITS OF MORPHEUS8

The Morpheus8 treatment provides enhancements for a broad range of aging skin concerns including fine lines, deeper wrinkles, sun damage, uneven texture, pigment irregularities, blood vessels and redness. This platform delivers improvements for aging skin that would typically require two, three, or even four different technologies. Besides its non-surgical anti-aging benefits, Morpheus8 also works to improve the visibility of stretch marks, active and non-active acne and scars. Another thing we love about Morpheus8 is that is comes with very little downtime. These treatments are an excellent accompaniment to fillers, Botox, other in-office services such as laser skin resurfacing and Ulthera or Diamond glow dermal infusions to give you the healthiest facial skin possible.

Laser Liposuction Procedure
When the Liposuction procedure is complete, we clothe our patient a special corset before s/he comes out of anestheisa. Thus we keep swellings and bruises at minimum level. Besides it will help body to take the desired shape during the healing period. The corset should be weared for 2-4 weeks except the times when taking shower. Post-op process is rather confortable and painless.
One of the greatest benefit of the procedure is to enable tightening and recovery of the skin. These benefits are the main reasons that this technique is created and used by the doctors. The other benefit of this procedure is that the healing process is quite fast.
Patients can return back to their daily lives after the same day of the operation, especially after liposunctions applied to a single area. In case of procedures which are applied to 2-3 areas, patients can return back to normal life after resting 3-4 days. Post-op bruises,swellings, time required for wearing corset and returning to daily routine is faster than classic techniques. The patient may start light workouts and exercises after 10th day. ─░t is recommended to start heavy workouts after 3rd week. Post-op bruises disappear between 10th and 14th day. Swellings caused by the operation decreases after 3rd week. By this means you can notice the differences in your body after the 3rd week. However, remember that the processs of reshaping will take 6 months to fully complete.

Laser Liposuction Procedure
When the Liposuction procedure is complete, we clothe our patient a special corset before s/he comes out of anestheisa. Thus we keep swellings and bruises at minimum level. Besides it will help body to take the desired shape during the healing period. The corset should be weared for 2-4 weeks except the times when taking shower. Post-op process is rather confortable and painless.
One of the greatest benefit of the procedure is to enable tightening and recovery of the skin. These benefits are the main reasons that this technique is created and used by the doctors. The other benefit of this procedure is that the healing process is quite fast.
Patients can return back to their daily lives after the same day of the operation, especially after liposunctions applied to a single area. In case of procedures which are applied to 2-3 areas, patients can return back to normal life after resting 3-4 days. Post-op bruises,swellings, time required for wearing corset and returning to daily routine is faster than classic techniques. The patient may start light workouts and exercises after 10th day. ─░t is recommended to start heavy workouts after 3rd week. Post-op bruises disappear between 10th and 14th day. Swellings caused by the operation decreases after 3rd week. By this means you can notice the differences in your body after the 3rd week. However, remember that the processs of reshaping will take 6 months to fully complete.
